About Me
Hello World! My name is Varun Mittal and I am a rising junior at James B. Conant High School. In my free time, I enjoy playing basketball and soccer, as well as spending time with my family.
About the Project
Title: Home Court Advantage, an examination into how much affect homecourt advantage really affects victories
Goals
Goal 1: To make something cool in R
Goal 2: To find an interesting trend/revelation using statistical examination with R
A complication of this could be my lack of sports data so far
“This is data science”
Preceptor Kane’s Free High School Data Science Bootcamp
